{"tid":2362002,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃圈辦室內新春市集自救","createTime":"2021-01-11T06:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T07:01:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0f2a4c4d8e358d54029e549cf3f8eefff4402121","tid":2362002,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:49:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210111/SDEJLLOAXBF67L4XW6EOPOREDE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210111%2FSDEJLLOAXBF67L4XW6EOPOREDE%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BegMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=3ac89ad5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210111%2FSDEJLLOAXBF67L4XW6EOPOREDE%2F&h=835ad133\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210111/SDEJLLOAXBF67L4XW6EOPOREDE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n黃圈辦室內新春市集自救<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5HdZUJSV9XBAUmanNLm-3dzMjqc=/886x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RLN3WYJUTFCSLNMPDXTGK6NJSI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5HdZUJSV9XBAUmanNLm-3dzMjqc%3D%2F886x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRLN3WYJUTFCSLNMPDXTGK6NJSI.jpg&h=6507e492&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■撐「喜」香港市集將部份收益捐贈612基金。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。。。。。，自發舉行撐「喜」香港市集，冀為同路人帶來一點溫飽，並重拾力量一同再出發。<br />\n<br />\n「HongKong_IN」將於年廿七至年三十在九龍區一個面積逾2,000呎的室內場地，舉辦「港嘢2.0 之 撐&ldquo;喜&rdquo;香港私人市集」。活動負責人光仔表示，籌備新春市集是因為「政府唔搞」，「佢要用呢啲伎倆阻止你去做反政府嘅嘢。以前乾貨最好賣嘅，係一啲諷刺時弊嘅嘢，佢連呢啲都唔畀出現。」而為免過早曝光遭受打壓，市集詳情稍後才公佈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n部份收益捐612基金<br />\n<br />\n年宵以撐「喜」香港為主題，光仔冀為同路人帶來正能量，「條路太漫長，係會有灰心、傷心嘅時候，但係咪真係要將負能量一起帶住呢？」疫下經濟轉差，光仔說很多同路人都等待「開飯」，他們用僅餘的資金創業，「搵餐飯食」，希望藉市集鼓勵他們。除了期望檔主得到溫飽，其他同路人亦會受惠。HongKong_IN會將收到的租金，以及檔主盈利的一成捐到612人道支援基金。<br />\n<br />\nHongKong_IN目前已收到逾30人認投檔主，超出預期攤檔數目。產品涵蓋文創、。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"192933f2573fd1186c9f09e2af3446c1506d315a","tid":2362002,"uid":23672,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:50:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01dbefee83cc238e870424509af428a41c093aca","tid":2362002,"uid":1608,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T07:01:31.000Z","msg":"到時班黑狗實踩場搞野<br />\n又話犯限聚乜乜乜<br />\n要諗諗點拆"}]}